name: Ultimate Tarot - 22 Majors Arcana - 13 Styles
description:
Trained with 13 sets of tarot cards (22 majors arcana). Each card was trained with their set name and card name.

Note that these card are often depicted with nude characters, although never explicitly.

Suggested prompt:

English text, roman numeral, card \(medium\)

Major arcanas names and typical prompt for such card:

The_Fool, 1boy,solo, holding white flower, dog, cliff, sky, happy

The_Magician, wizard, red, fire, robe

The_Priestess, 1girl, cross, robe, mitre, candle, chalice

The_Empress, 1girl, sitting, majestic, crown, dress, full body, looking at viewer

The_Emperor, 1boy, sitting, majestic, crown, robe, scepter, full body, looking at viewer

The_Hierophant, sitting, cross, robe, mitre, book

The_Lovers, 1boy, 1girl, nude, hug, couple

The_Chariot, 1boy, horse, horse riding, chariot

The_Strength, solo, lion, outdoor

The_Hermit, old man, lantern, dark

Wheel_Of_Fortune, wheel, abstract, animals, symbols

Justice, balance scale, sword,

The_Hanged_Man, 1boy, upside down,

Death, skeleton, horse riding, multiple boys, dark,

Temperance, angel, cup, water,

The_Devil, devil, horn, 1boy, 1girl, pentagram

The_Tower, tower, explosion, 1girl, 1boy, falling, fire, sky

The_Star, star (symbol), water, nude

The_Moon, moon, animals, crayfish, water, sky

The_Sun, sun, sky, sun rays

Judgment, multiple boys, multiple girls, scared, sky, angel, cloud, trumpet

The_World, abstract, circle, world, symbol, animals, nude, outstretched arms

Throw those in a wildcard txt file for an AI generated tarot seance :)

Set name and suggested prompt:

(8bit:1.2),pixelated,pixel art

(After:1.2),retro artstyle, flat color

(AGOT:1.2),drawing

(CelticTarot:1.2), intricate border

(CosmicTarot:1.2), retro artstyle

(DruidTarot:1.2)

(GreenWitch:1.2)

(HolyGrailTarot:1.2),retro artstyle

(MangaTarot:1.2)

(MLTSTarot:1.2), flat color, retro artstyle

(MorganGreerTarot:1.2), retro artstyle, thick outline

(OlympusTarot:1.2), thick border, intricate border, retro artstyle

(SacredIsleTarot:1.2), vivid colors, intricate details

DruidTarot, CosmicTarot and Sacred Isle are my favorites.
